rget=\"_blank\">http://www.chainreactioncycles.com/hk/en</a><br />\nWiggle:<a href=\"http://www.wiggle.co.uk/cycle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.co.uk%2Fcycle&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=dc9995de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wiggle.co.uk/cycle</a> <br />\n單車快遞:<a href=\"http://www.cyclingexpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyclingexpress.com&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=666a98dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cyclingexpress.com</a><br />\nBike24:<a href=\"http://www.bike24.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bike24.com&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=e0d3618f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bike24.com</a><br />\n<br />\n二手:<br />\n各大FB二手谷(不一一詳列)<br />\n28Bike: <a href=\"http://www.28bike.com/classifieds/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.28bike.com%2Fclassifieds%2Findex.php&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=80218de5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.28bike.com/classifieds/index.php</a>"},{"pid":"4d99d91d08f6790a5b42859f8d92635fb7c15e83","tid":2488914,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"引自B-LJJ_(共用) 巴打嘅落斜心得 <br />\n<br />\n的確冇手套 包兩層把布 <br />\n同埋落斜唔駛hold 到支把實晒, hold 住下把, 前臂同地面平行, 手唔駛hold 到實, 你感覺到你隻手啱啱hi 到支把就得, 屎忽同樣道理, 雙腳俾少少力企落對踏度, 屎忽感覺到啱啱hi 到個saddle, 攞啱方向就由得架車自己去, 必要時輕輕修正, 唔駛同架車鬥力, 架車行起左有慣性, 速度越快慣性越大架車其實越定; 入彎, 雙手hold 得支把firm 少少, 依然唔係同佢鬥力, 攞正個方向, 向彎心隻腳喺12 點另一隻腳踩實6 點, 將體重放喺向彎心隻手同踩實6 點隻腳, 重心稍為向彎心移, 方法有兩個: 1. 向彎心隻腳膝頭向彎心方向擺. 2. 屎忽向彎心方向移少少成份人向彎心擺少少; 將視線集中喺你想架車去既方向, 望遠少少; 最重要係要brake 既話入彎前好俾定, 入彎後要再俾brake 既話都只限於輕輕印落去就好, 唔好揸波咁一野揸落去, 唔係你會派得好開心 <br />\n試多幾次熟練左落斜就會又安全又好玩 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梅子林震撚到傻狗也不屌<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"f0946f2b46a8c3c4e5877a6fd43bb493f205d20e","tid":2488914,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"基本公路車訓練方式<br />\n(好多人有好多種唔同既訓練,唔一定死跟其中一種)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下<br />\nby 矮仔落樓梯<br />\n<br />\nInterval Training 有好多種<br />\n但不外乎FTP Ride, Cadence Drill, Sprint Flat-out 幾種<br />\n可以mix&amp;match<br />\n有好多都係係GCN學返黎,但可以因應自己情況同踩嘅路調整<br />\n<br />\n以我用開嘅interval為例<br />\nFTP Ride 即係針對提升帶氧界限功率嘅訓練, 最簡單嘅方法係直接踩FTP,休息,FTP,休息之類嘅pattern<br />\n又或者做&quot;Sweet Spot&quot;, 即係80%~95% FTP<br />\n另外有種叫over/under,即係90%同110% FTP 輪流做<br />\nFTP系列interval 對於爬坡能力有幫助<br />\n<br />\nCadence Drill 即係針對係相同輸出嘅下使用唔同cadence嘅能力<br />\n60,70,80,90,100,110,120,130一格格升上去,再落返黎,然後加高功率再黎過<br />\n再於唔同情況適合唔同Cadence, Cadence Drill 訓練嘅係腿肌肉力量同速度去適應唔同環境, 對平路均速相當有效<br />\n<br />\nFlat-out, 或者通常叫做sprint session 係以短至10,30秒無氧衝刺同休息做間隔嘅訓練<br />\n冇咩好講,即係訓練你衝刺加速嘅能力,比賽用多<br />\n<br />\n頭先提過可以mix&amp;match, 好多時候係FTP Ride 入面都會加啲Flat-out 入去令件事冇咁悶,同埋令自己能力更加全面<br />\n又或者over/under用同一齒比但係over用高cadence, under用自然cadence之類<br />\n好多配搭好多玩法<br />\n<br />\n當然唔好唔記得加warm up warm down 同記得拉筋 <br />\n早兩三年踩車冇乜點練過踩平路上28都keep唔到耐<br />\n今年2月開始用interval 操車<br />\n依家唔洗點俾力就去到30以上 <br />\n爬沙田坳道法藏寺上札山亭一腳到avg8kmh<br />\n雖然仲係雞腳,不過同以前比進步好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買咗pm再講"},{"pid":"a1dcd572fd81cb15e362c943738e0288add1dbfb","tid":2488914,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"LIHKG STRAVA GP:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.strava.com/clubs/LIHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.strava.com%2Fclubs%2FLIHKG&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=2fe5c447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.strava.com/clubs/LIHKG</a><br />\n<br />\n連登巴絲帶戰車列表<br />\n戰車LIST：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/rNcrtq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FrNcrtq&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=76fb170e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/rNcrtq</a><br />\n戰車LIST加名：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/80rf0U\" data-sr-url=\"ht